    "course_title": "COMMUNITY PSYCHIATRY ELECTIVE",
    "description": "Immersive experience in community mental health while embedded within a community support team, either at Gateway or Community Treatment Alternatives (CTA).  Gateway is an assertive community treatment team serving Dane County residents who have severe mental illness and substance abuse issues.  CTA is an assertive community treatment team that works exclusively with adults involved in the criminal justice system. Patients must be either diverted from the Dane County Jail or be conditionally released after being found \"not guilty by reason of mental disease or defect\" (NGI).",
